{"tid":1014816,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"負離子係無。撚。用。㗎","createTime":"2019-02-09T13:32:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-09T15:28:38.000Z","uid":138409,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6134d199a3ad667bdb5a113d19e5cf7a78dbd9e7","tid":1014816,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T13:32:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZQ--scjcAZ4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DZQ--scjcAZ4&d=6BLFUKkZTytPAocRz50jI6arsW1wokO1n9cqNe5yO8o%3D&h=b6a56a66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZQ--scjcAZ4</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">tl;dr<br />\n</span></span><br />\n基本上支持負離子好處嘅研究<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">研究方法上大部分都有問題</span>，例如sample size 太細、又或者未能排除係安慰劑效應<br />\n而且由於空氣中負離子高嘅地方，正好係大自然中如瀑布/海灘等地區<br />\n負離子表面上對情緒有正面影響，<br />\n好大機會只係因為自然環境本身對情緒有正面影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n有關負離子作用有大量研究，以下係review /meta-analysis<br />\n<br />\nAir ions and mood outcomes: a review and meta-analysis.<br />\nPerez V, Alexander DD, Bailey WH.<br />\nBMC Psychiatry. 2013 Jan 15;13:29.<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/23320516\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpubmed%2F23320516&d=6BLFUKkZTytPAocRz50jI6arsW1wokO1n9cqNe5yO8o%3D&h=a17a7fdc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/23320516</a><br />\n<br />\nAir ions and respiratory function outcomes: a comprehensive review<br />\nDominik D Alexander, William H Bailey, Vanessa Perez, Meghan E Mitchell, and Steave Su<br />\nJ Negat Results Biomed. 2013; 12: 14.<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3848581/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC3848581%2F&d=6BLFUKkZTytPAocRz50jI6arsW1wokO1n9cqNe5yO8o%3D&h=55ceb1b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3848581/</a><br />\n<br />\nExposure of laboratory animals to small air ions: a systematic review of biological and behavioral studies.<br />\nBailey WH, Williams AL, Leonhard MJ.<br />\nBiomed Eng Online. 2018 Jun 5; 17(1):72.<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/29866122\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpubmed%2F29866122&d=6BLFUKkZTytPAocRz50jI6arsW1wokO1n9cqNe5yO8o%3D&h=37d2a16e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/29866122</a>"},{"pid":"3fffad4a98c4cdd8fd6522f4e91505e7d21a77a3","tid":1014816,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T13:35:57.000Z","msg":"負離子(Negative Ion)本身只係Marketing term<br />\n90年代尾無啦啦學術化<br />\n明明學術上係叫陰離子(Anion)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"014dc3cdd38a540e49cfab3c55d7153cc0bd0dce","tid":1014816,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T13:36:12.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"056c20eb8051483b5530579518bea698639153cd","tid":1014816,"uid":93646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T13:36:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8b068c7d9376c1c7d894cbeee467683325e07c54","tid":1014816,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"056c20eb8051483b5530579518bea698639153cd","tid":1014816,"uid":93646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T13:36:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T15:16:32.000Z","msg":"對人體完全無害"},{"pid":"00eb81c60a750fd49e95e2021432b3ca8f45832b","tid":1014816,"uid":69841,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T15:28:38.000Z","msg":"睇topic以為話負離子電唔到直髮"}]}